column5: I eagerly await your contribution to the 'extra cost of fishing' thread!  Lol
I've had that pair for 5 years now.  Great pair of glasses!
yep great glasses, I had the same pair last year but I lost them one the first day
Best fishing glasses I have ever worn, wont go without them!!!

I dropped my Maui's on the floor in a shoppers drugmart when a worker came through a door in front me then turned around and came at me. Needless to say I shattered a lens when they hit the floor. They need to go back to Maui for replacement lenses. Definitely the best glasses I have worn.
I also have those Maui Jims + a pair of these for driving .. love them.  http://www.mauijim.com/shop/en/us/mens-sunglasses/stingray?showImage=103-02
